						<br>
						<br>	
						My inspiration comes from amazing abilities displayed by the biological systems of nature.
						I aspire to bring robotic systems on par with biological counterparts in terms of perception, movement and control.
						<br>
						I am eager to explore the following research topics
						<ul>
							<li>Dynamic locomotion and manipulation</li>
							<li>Optimization for control and motion planning of robots</li>
							<li>Learning applied bridging perception and control</li>
						</ul>
